Package net.fabricmc.fabric.api.object.builder.v1.client.model

Class FabricModelPredicateProviderRegistry

java.lang.Object
net.fabricmc.fabric.api.object.builder.v1.client.model.FabricModelPredicateProviderRegistry
@Deprecated public final class FabricModelPredicateProviderRegistry extends Object
Deprecated.
Replaced by access wideners for ModelPredicateProviderRegistry registration methods in Fabric Transitive Access Wideners (v1).
Allows registering model predicate providers for item models.

A registered model predicate providers for an item can be retrieved through ModelPredicateProviderRegistry.get(Item, Identifier).
